quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Rivalry diverted you
  102,2,until you stopped by the cemetery
  102,3,No indeed! You will know
  102,4,"Again, no indeed! You will know"
  102,5,No indeed! If you will know with the knowledge of certainty
  102,6,"you will, certainly, see hellfire"
  102,7,"Again, you will see it with the eye of certainty"
  102,8,"Again, you will, certainly, be asked on that day about the bliss"